SUMMARY="A clone of the well known game Pac-Man"
DESCRIPTION="You must run through the maze to eat all pills without being captured \
by a ghost. By eating an energizer, Kapman gets the ability to eat ghosts for a few \
seconds. When a stage is cleared of pills and energizer the player is taken to the \
next stage with slightly increased game speed."
